OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright morning with hazy
OL,6,Fsunny spells. Cloud will tend to
OL,7,Fdevelop through the day and bring a
OL,8,Ffew showers, some of which may be on
OL,9,Fthe heavy side.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThere will be a mixture of
OL,12,Fclear intervals and showers, these
OL,13,Fmore frequent over Perthshire and the
OL,14,FTrossachs in the evening and early
OL,15,Fnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FAnother mixed day with some
OL,18,Fbrighter spells but also some showers,
OL,19,Fwhich may become slow moving and bring
OL,20,Fsome longer spells of rain to Angus
OL,21,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
